Main areas

Source: R/mainareaFdir2018-datadoc.R
mainareaFdir2018.Rd

Definition for area coding system defined by the Norwegian directorate of Fisheries (2018 revision). This revision has been in use for their fishery statistics as of 2018 (inclusive). Polygons are defined in WGS84 coordinates (unprojected).

data(mainareaFdir2018)

Format

SpatialPolygonsDataFrame with area names identified in the column 'polygonName'. See StratumPolygon.

Examples

 data(mainareaFdir2018)
 sp::plot(mainareaFdir2018)
